        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Colorado_2/_scene_bull.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5b54d9fb-fa85-4302-a8d5-c5c5e97344c4).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon 47,\rThe mexican government has discovered the assasination plot being devised by the paramilitary group headed by Sean Rose and Maya Parvati both of whom are known international terrorists. Their training location has been tracked to Colorado and subsequently on request of the Mexican government the elimination of every individual involved in this plot has been green lighted by the ICA. On a side note the client has requested to mask all eliminations as &quot;accidents&quot;.\rGood Luck 47.",
